Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,After unifying the northern realms —
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:24.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— Cao Cao ordered to build "Bronze Sparrow Terrace" on the bank of the Zhang-River —
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:28.40,Note (Potential Style),,0,0,0,,Note: "Bronze Sparrow Terrace" (铜雀台) was a real terrace located in Yè-city, Hebei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:28.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— to commemorate his great achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:33.42,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He garrisoned his troops around Xǔchāng and fiefed them land to cultivate, to build up their strength-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:40.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— and prepare for his expedition southwards: First to conquer the Jing-Province, then take lands of Wú.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:45.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei turned to Liu Biao in Jing-Province\Nafter his defeat at Runan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:48.62,Thinking,,0,0,0,,When Cao Cao warring in the north, \NXǔchāng was weakly defended.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:53.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei proposed an attack on Xǔchāng several times —
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:55.92,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— but his proposals were never accepted by Liu Biao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:00.86,Thinking,,0,0,0,,In the spring of the 12th year of Jian'an period*—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:00.86,Note (Potential Style),,0,0,0,,*207 AD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:06.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,—Liu Biao's surrendered generals, Zhang Wu and Chen Sun, rebelled at Jiangxia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:11.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei led Guan Yu, Zhang Fei, and Zhao Yun\Non a punitive expedition—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:15.19,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— and crushed the rebellion of Chen Sun and Zhang Wu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Zǐlóng, you truly are a valiant warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:21.78,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(235.956,701.03)}Zhào Yún \NStyled: Zǐlóng
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuande.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done a marvelous job.\NThe rebellion at Jiangxia has been crushed—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:49.64,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,500,3700,4500)\pos(214.334,759.358)}Liú Bèi\N Styled: Xuándé
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,— and the people can live in peace.\NI must say that all the credit should go to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:52.86,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,500,5700,6500)\pos(1181.284,737.44)}Liú Biǎo \NStyled: Jǐngshēng
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared a banquet in your honor\Nto celebrate the triumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I serve under your command.\NIt is my duty to repay your kindness with gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After you, brother Jǐngshēng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good horse.\NA great horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.54,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(201.933,741.244)}Cài Mào\NStyled: Déguī
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This was Zhang Wu's horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A good horse indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, since you like this horse this much, \Nthen I'd like to offer it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:32.75,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(434.89,751.977)}Zhāng Fēi\NStyled: Yìdé
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! My brother, that will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:40.11,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1194.037,699.763)}Guān Yǔ\NStyled: Yúncháng
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:06:03.11,Note (Potential Style),,0,0,0,,Note: The choreography depicts the characters "迎皇叔" or "Welcome, Uncle."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.24,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1138.787,675.398)}Yī Jí\NStyled: Jībó
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}With your great talent\NJing-Province can be safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}Though the rebellion of Jiangxia has been crushed —
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}— the nine commanderies and forty-two counties of Jing aren't free from outside disturbances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}\NAttacks and harassments by \Nthe Nanyue are still troubling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}And the strong forces of {\i1}Zhāng Lǔ {\i0}and{\i1} Sūn Quán{\i0}\Nhave only added to my worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}You don't need to worry,\Nmy three warrior-generals will be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}Zhang Fei can guard the southern border along Nanyue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}Guan Yu can defend the city of Guzi \Nto be a deterrent force to Zhang Lu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}And Zhao Yun can patrol {\i1}the Three Rivers{\i0}\N to watch out for Sun Quan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:27.90,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: The Three Rivers aka. Sānjiāng
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.983,998.561)}{\bord14.265}So brother, are you still worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.983,998.561)}{\bord14.265}Well in that case, Jing-Province will be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.62,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That Liu Bei harbors ill will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:43.10,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He had to come to Jing-Province after his defeat by Cao Cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He had nowhere else to seek refuge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Today he came back in triumph, and tried his best to win the favor of my brother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, he managed to appoint three of \Nhis warrior-generals to important posts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the defense of Jing-Province —
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.58,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(255.815,641.933)}Lady Cài
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,— has fallen into the hands of Liu Bei and has subordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei's generals are at three key strategic positions, while he himself stays here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As I see it, the longer this goes, the more disastrous it will be for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've often heard from your brother-in-law —
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that Liu Bei is a man of profound ambition and a great shrewdness, like a closed book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you must prevent my brother-in-law —
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,— from handing over Jing-Province to Liu Bei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:27.63,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Attendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look for a chance to persuade my brother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Attendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I lying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You got drunk at the banquet and was brought back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I was in high spirits. \NI guess I did drink a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I find you've indeed become muddle-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, why would you entrust the defense of Jing-Province to outsiders so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you've assigned the defense of Jing-Province to the three generals under Liu Bei's command.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,His men are all valiant and fierce. I like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you trust other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that since his arrival in Jing-Province, Liu Bei has been getting along with the officials and officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be caught off guard by this kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, he's assigned his generals to important places.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,While he himself remains in the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything should go wrong one day, how would you deal with all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei is a kind and righteous person\NLet us not suspect him without evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,After Liu Bei's defeat at Runan, none of the lords dared to shelter him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody had kindness like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be for the best to send Liu Bei out of Jing-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good horse!\NTruly a good horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This horse must not be ridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.983,998.561)}{\bord14.265}Lord, this horse has "tear tracks" under its eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.983,998.561)}{\bord14.265}Its name is {\i1}'Dilu'{\i0}. It will harm its rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.983,998.561)}{\bord14.265}Zhang Wu died because of this horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.983,998.561)}{\bord14.265}My lord should never ride it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.983,998.561)}{\bord14.265}My lord—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.983,998.561)}{\bord14.265}"Dilu" is a good horse indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}However, good horses should be used for close combat on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}Liu Xuande is a veteran warrior of countless battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}As the saying goes: \NA treasured horse matches only a gallant warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}It will be proper to offer back the horse\Nto its master, Liu Xuande.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you come here for, my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been sitting all day doing nothing, \Nso I've come here to practice riding to pass the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.983,998.561)}{\bord14.265}If you find days dragging on—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}— you could lead your troops to {\i1}Xinye County{\i0} in {\i1}Xiāngyáng{\i0}, and station them there for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}It's a prosperous place with ample provisions to support a battalion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:12:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}Besides, staying still for too long would only be a waste of your martial talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}I'm grateful for that great steed you gave me the other day—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}— but you are a soldier, fighting on the battlefield. You need a great steed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}I shouldn't have taken the horse away from you.\NSo I give it back to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I can't but take the horse back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Lord Xuande.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,May I know your name, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}Yī Jí{\i0},\Nan apparitor of Jing-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you'd like to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,General, this horse must not be ridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave it to Lord Liu Biao, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he has returned it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}That is because Kuǎi Yuè told Lord Liu Biao  —
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}that this horse is named "Dilu" and it will harm its rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}That's why Lord Liu Biao returned the horse\Nback to you. How can you ride it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}Thank you for your kindness, I did not know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}However, everyone has his destiny. How can a horse change it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}You're known as a kindhearted and righteous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}If you don't mind,\NI'd like to pay a visit to you at Xinye some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, you're flattering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome at my place any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so kind.\NGoodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A few days ago, Lady Gān dreamed that she had swallowed the stars of the Big Dipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, this is a good omen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:57.10,Note (Potential Style),,0,0,0,,Note: The turtle-shells and sticks on Sun Qian's table are part of historical Chinese divination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:58.41,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1166.324,701.075)}Sūn Qián\NStyled: Gōngyòu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby to be born\Nmust be a man of great expectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a good omen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You are about to get an honorable son! \NMy congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and find out if the baby is a boy or a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a boy! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Things turned out as expected!\NMy congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, my elder brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My elder brother, give a name to my nephew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, think of a name with good omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Let's think of a name... think of a name...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since my lady dreamed of swallowing the Big Dipper —
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we may give him the name {\i1}Ēdǒu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:04.19,Note (Potential Style),,0,0,0,,*(or  Ādǒu. "Dǒu" means the Big Dipper)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, my elder brother! You now have a son, and the Hàn Dynasty has a successor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and have a look at my nephew!\NLet's go! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuande, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks, sir!\NIt's kind of you to come to me in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for not coming to meet you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu Biao sent me\Nto invite you to Jing-Province for a talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother, I see you are getting light-headed.\NWe'd better stop drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You are better than me.\NI have no one to talk to about my worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NIf there is anything the matter, you can just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}Cao Cao is in the capital of Xǔ with his soldiers back from his northern conquests.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}The Yuán clan of Hebei have all been eliminated —
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}— Cao Cao must have already begun planning to taking over the Jing-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}Back then, I didn't heed your advice and attack Cao Cao while he was away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}I lost a good opportunity. Now how much I regret!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}My brother, there is no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}Right now, the Empire is still in disarray.\NWar breaks out everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}There will be other opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}Brother, why are you so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265} I have been trying to tell you my worries.\NBut I have never had a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265} You don't have to worry.\NIf I am of any help to you —
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}— By hook or by crook, I will do anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}I am worried about my two sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}My former wife gave birth to my first son, {\i1}Liú Qí.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}He is virtuous, but too weak and timid to manage the state affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}My second wife gave birth to my younger son,{\i1} Liú Cóng.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}He's a bright boy, I like him very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}If I set aside the elder and make the younger my successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}I'd be going against the way of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}If I name the elder as my successor,\Nwhat can I do with the Cài Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}The military power in Jing-Province is in their hands —
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}— and they are sure to cause trouble in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}That's why I'm wavering and can't make the decision, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}This is a matter of your family. \NIt needs to be considered carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}My interference would be improper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}We're just like brothers.\NI hope you'll speak without reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}Choosing the successor is of extreme importance. One should never act impetuously.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:20:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}Since the ancient times, removing the elder and choosing the younger—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}—has been the source of disaster. Endless trouble will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}If you're worried about the Cai-clan's power,\Nyou could reduce it a bit at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}You can't make the younger the successor only because you dote on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}The days and months are slipping by, and I'm becoming old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}But my great deeds are still to be accomplished...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}I hear that while you were in Xǔchāng —
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}—you and Cao Cao talked about heroes over green plums and wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}You proposed many famous men of our present time —
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}—but Cao Cao just said that: 'There are only two heroes of these lands, you and himself.'
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:21:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}With all his power and influence，\NCao Cao didn't place himself before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}Why do you have to worry about great deeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}My only hurdle is that I don't have any armies or land.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}To tell you the truth—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}— if I had a real solid base, the lesser men of the world are indeed not worth worrying over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight at midnight,\NI will send men to surround Liu Bei's guest-house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll kill him first and then tell my brother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure not to leak this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured, my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, sir, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in such a panic?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuande—you're still kept in the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Cai Mao has sent troops to kill you{\i1} tonight!{\i0} Please return to Xīnyě immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Biao knows nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cais plans to act first and report later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no time for hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.22,0:22:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I go without saying goodbye to Brother Jingsheng?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, you will be killed by Cai's men for certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I will repay your kindness in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-Be quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Search it!\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.06,0:22:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who leaked our plans?\NLiu Bei must have gotten away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:10.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}"Too long, far too long. I have been stuck—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:14.02,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}—gazing at the old mountains and rivers day by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:16.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}{\pos(707.983,998.561)}A dragon can never be kept in a pond—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:18.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.265}—he should ride on the thunder to heaven and beyond."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill this ingrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been with Xuande quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen him write poems.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.48,0:23:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be a plot by someone else to drive a wedge between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother-in-law, a person's heart is unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting Liu Bei go is like releasing a tiger into wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go to Xinye and catch Liu Bei at once\Nto avoid future trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,0:24:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be reckless. There's no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We must not lose the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.46,0:24:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you release a tiger into wilderness!\NTomorrow, it will be too late to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.42,0:25:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.92,0:25:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter from Lord Liu Biao.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.86,0:25:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.49,0:25:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.22,0:25:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My three brothers, Mr Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.76,0:25:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu Biao has sent me a letter —
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.54,0:25:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,— asking me to preside over the Harvest Festival in Xiāngyáng on his behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.82,0:25:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.02,0:25:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...\NWhy can't he himself preside over the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.10,0:25:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jingsheng is not in good health recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.54,0:25:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,His two sons are too young.\NHe is afraid of a violation of etiquette if they preside.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.82,0:25:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I am asked to preside on his behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.66,0:26:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day, you returned in a hurry from Jing-Province, disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.61,0:26:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think something must have gone wrong in Jing-Province.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.27,0:26:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go to this festival without preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.22,0:26:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When Brother Jingsheng and I had a drink, I made an indiscreet remark
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.34,0:26:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But Brother Jingsheng didn't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.46,0:26:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Lady Cai and Cai Mao tried to murder me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.10,0:26:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Yi Ji's timely warning,\NI was able to escape to Xīnyě before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.26,0:27:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's invitation to the festival...\NI do not know how it will turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.14,0:27:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You suspect that you made an indiscreet remark, but Lord Liu Biao didn't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.12,0:27:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't easily trust words of outsiders
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.34,0:27:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiāngyáng is not far away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.78,0:27:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't go, Lord Liu Biao will genuinely become suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.70,0:27:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yunchang has a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.93,0:27:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother, one can't be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.94,0:27:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no 'good' banquets.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.94,0:27:28.54,Note (Potential Style),,0,0,0,,*Alludes to the Hongmen Banquet
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.54,0:27:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better not to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.66,0:27:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My two elder brothers both have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.66,0:27:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't go, Lord Liu Biao would be suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.72,0:27:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go, Cai Mao might intend to murder you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.62,0:27:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, I think you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.18,0:27:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will lead three hundred soldiers to escort you and make sure nothing happens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.26,0:27:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.18,0:28:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass on my orders:\NNothing is to be told to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.76,0:28:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who disobey will be put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.30,0:28:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.70,0:28:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,General.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.10,0:28:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,General. Seeing your actions,\NI feel something is going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.14,0:28:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei is a 'mighty raptor' of our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.14,0:28:29.74,Note (Potential Style),,0,0,0,,Note: A "Mighty Raptor" or "Xiāoxióng"(枭雄) is a term used for fierce, ambitious and formidable "great men" of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.72,0:28:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be a source of trouble if he stays here long.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.22,0:28:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to kill him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.90,0:28:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.12,0:28:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, the officials from the nine commanderies and forty-two counties are all at the banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.48,0:28:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an act may make lose their favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.18,0:28:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have secret orders from my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.10,0:28:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case, we will do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.30,0:28:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The east, north and south gates of Xiāngyáng city\Nare guarded by my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.34,0:29:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the west gate is left open, \Nbecause the Tán-Creek blocks the passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.62,0:29:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with tens of thousands of troops,\None could not get across that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.18,0:29:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If Liu Bei's officers follow and protect him, it would be hard to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.46,0:29:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already placed five hundred men in ambush inside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.42,0:29:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell Wén Pìn and Wang Wei —
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.48,0:29:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,— to arrange another table in the outer hall\Nand treat the officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.50,0:29:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,First, separate Liu Bei from his officers.\NThen you can strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.14,0:29:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.48,0:29:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.46,0:29:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.42,0:29:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.22,0:30:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.10,0:30:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu, excuse me for not coming to meet you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.42,0:30:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,General Cai, you are so kind.\NExcuse me for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.82,0:30:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.78,0:30:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhao, this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.26,0:30:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu, this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.22,0:30:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, my father is feeling unwell and could not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.14,0:30:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The officials from the counties are all present. Please preside at the ceremonies on his behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.90,0:30:35.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(218.438,570.607)}Liú Cóng
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.02,0:30:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.66,0:30:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I normally wouldn't dare undertake such a heavy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.70,0:30:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But since it's my brother's order—
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.74,0:30:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,—I dare not refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.58,0:30:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirs, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.48,0:30:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.06,0:30:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.58,0:31:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.58,0:31:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.58,0:31:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu, please.\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.95,0:31:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu, please.\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.82,0:31:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.02,0:31:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The banquet is ready in the side chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.16,0:31:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and your presence is expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.02,0:31:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you two generals, but you don't need to mind me.\NI can't drink alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.53,0:32:00.83,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(222.409,719.371)}Wén Pìn\NStyled:Zhòng Yè)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.58,0:32:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu.\NThe officers would like to drink with General Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.08,0:32:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you say to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.48,0:32:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zilong. Yes, it's ok to listen to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.82,0:32:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a seat at the banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.48,0:32:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.54,0:32:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.22,0:32:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My two young lords, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.78,0:32:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.50,0:32:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhao, please
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.91,0:32:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.54,0:32:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Two young lords, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.58,0:32:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhao, have some more wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.74,0:32:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. You too, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.65,0:32:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhao, have some more drinks please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.30,0:32:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhao, have some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.30,0:33:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,General Cai, everything is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.02,0:33:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.94,0:33:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When the drum is beat, you will all strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.42,0:33:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let Liu Bei get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.66,0:33:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.65,0:33:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.25,0:33:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.48,0:33:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.45,0:33:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, General Zhao!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.05,0:33:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle—please!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.62,0:33:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My two young lords, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.82,0:33:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhao, have another cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.14,0:33:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,May I show you the restroom, Lord Xuande?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.78,0:33:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A toast to General Zhao!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.98,0:33:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Have another cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.07,0:33:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you even have another? Haha!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.00,0:33:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.80,0:33:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, please do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.68,0:33:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Another toast to General Zhao!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.98,0:33:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, General Zhao, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.08,0:33:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhao, please finish this cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.28,0:34:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good, good, good! Hahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.26,0:34:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cai Mao has planned to murder you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.98,0:34:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers have laid an ambush in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.60,0:34:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The east, north and south gates of the city are heavily guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.85,0:34:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the west gate is left open.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.22,0:34:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You should leave here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.90,0:34:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.73,0:34:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.53,0:34:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, General Zhao, drink! Drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.60,0:34:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.66,0:34:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.87,0:34:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Report to General Cai\NLiu Bei rode out of the west gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.85,0:34:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.74,0:35:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Be sure to capture Liu Bei! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.80,0:35:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhao, have another glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.26,0:35:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, chase him!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.61,0:35:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dilu, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.48,0:35:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.10,0:36:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei, stop! Don't let Liu Bei escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.48,0:36:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dilu, Dilu, why do you harm your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.06,0:36:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Get into the water! \NCatch Liu Bei!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.93,0:36:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.23,0:36:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.03,0:36:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dilu!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.56,0:36:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,General Cai, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.80,0:36:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Bei!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.60,0:36:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life ends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.74,0:36:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dilu, Dilu, you indeed harmed your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.50,0:36:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Heaven is helping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.48,0:37:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Liu, why are you running away from the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.85,0:37:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cai Mao!\NWe have no grudge against each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.50,0:37:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you wish for my death!?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.06,0:37:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I ... I have no such intention!\ND–don't be misled by others!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.40,0:37:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cai Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.52,0:38:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord is an invited guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.58,0:38:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you chasing him with troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.75,0:38:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.48,0:38:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's left the banquet. I don't know where he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.62,0:38:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.54,0:38:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no sight of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.98,0:38:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go on looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.54,0:38:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't find him,\NI will come back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.77,0:38:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.10,0:39:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,General, you must be Liu Xuande. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.46,0:39:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Country lad, how do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.18,0:39:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.30,0:39:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But my teacher often talks with his visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.86,0:39:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They say Liu Xuande is a hero of the age, and he would pass here recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.48,0:39:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I find you look like the person they talk about, that's why I asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.18,0:39:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's your teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.42,0:39:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}My master is {\i1}Sīmǎ Huī{\i0}.\NHis style name is Décāo. He's from Yǐngchuān.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.32,0:39:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\pos(699,998)}His Daoist title is{\i1} Master Shuǐjìng{\i0}.*
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.34,0:40:00.03,Note (Potential Style),,0,0,0,,*Water Mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.03,0:40:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\pos(699,998)}Among his many friends —
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.38,0:40:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}— there are {\i1}Páng Dégōng{\i0} \Nand{\i1} Páng Tǒng{\i0}  from Xiangyang.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.42,0:40:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\pos(699,998)}And who are these two Pángs?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.32,0:40:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\pos(699,998)}They're uncle and nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.94,0:40:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\i1}Páng Dégōng{\i0}, style name {\i1}Shanming{\i0},\Nis ten years older than my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.76,0:40:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318\i1}Páng Tǒng{\i0}, style name {\i1}Shìyuán{\i0},\N he is five yours younger than my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.64,0:40:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}My master is very fond of Páng Tǒng\Nand calls him his younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.48,0:40:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your master now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.54,0:40:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the cottage in the woods right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.58,0:40:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come with me, General Liu.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.50,0:40:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.66,0:40:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice place!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.54,0:41:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The melody is so beautiful.\NWe may as well listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.02,0:41:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.74,0:41:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A high note suddenly rang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.22,0:41:58.96,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(351.485,725.484)}Sīmǎ Huī\NStyled: Décāo)
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.42,0:42:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It suggests that a hero must be listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.26,0:42:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my master, Master Shuijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.38,0:42:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, today you're fortunate to have a narrow escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.66,0:42:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come in and have a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.66,0:42:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If sir would please.
